Data availability

            The data used to make the analysis and produce the figures can be found at Zenodo (https://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.13768758)81. Source data are provided with this paper.
          Code availability

            The code to extrapolate the CMIP6 data to the stereographic grid can be found at Zenodo (https://zenodo.org/records/12755910)53. All other code used to produce the analysis and the figures is available in the same Zenodo repository as the data (https://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.13768758)81.
